What is the projected market size & growth rate of the Acrylic Surface Coating Market?

Market Analysis and Insights :

Global Acrylic Surface Coating Market

The acrylic surface coating market will reach at an estimated value of USD 71.63 billion and grow at a rate of 8.00% for the forecast period of 2021 to 2028. Rise in the demand for acrylic protective coatings on the industrial tools and equipment and decorative parts in building and construction industry is a vital factor driving the growth of acrylic surface coating market.

Acrylic surface coatings are defined as the paints that dry fast and it consists of pigments which are suspended in an acrylic polymer emulsion. These coatings are manufactured using acrylic or methacrylic polymer as it possesses strong color retention features. Powder coating, solvent-borne coating, and waterborne coating are numerous technologies which are used for manufacturing acrylic surface coating in the acrylic surface coatings industry globally.

Rise in the investments in infrastructure development activities in developing economies is the vital factor escalating the market growth, also rise in the favorable government regulations and green environmental regulations, rising demand from the numerous applications which includes exterior and interior wall decoration, automobiles, traffic lights, furniture among others, rise in the investments in infrastructure development activities in developing economies and rise in the demand in light of high disposable income and urbanization along with rapid infrastructural development are the major factors among others driving the acrylic surface coating market. Moreover, rising research and development activities in the market and rising demand from the emerging economies will further create new opportunities for the acrylic surface coating market in the forecast period of 2021- 2028.

However, rise in the stringent regulations pertaining to solvent-borne acrylic surface coatings are the major factors among others acting as restraints, and will further challenge the growth of acrylic surface coating market in the forecast period mentioned above.

